  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1804_brd_ac_r.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="per" type="endorsements" rend="top centre"><p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
            <gap/>
            <unclear>الله</unclear> 
            فدوی پادشاه غازی 
            <persName ref="#muhammadShah">محمد شاه</persName>
            </mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Black ink seal<mentioned><gap/> servant of the Emperor <persName ref="#muhammadShah">Muhammad Shah</persName></mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقرار کرد و اعتراف صحیح شرعی نمود مخبر باسم و نسب خود مسمی
               <persName ref="#sultanKhan">سلطان خان</persName>
               <lb/>ولد جهان خان ابن چهتر خان افغان غوری معه
               <persName ref="#haiyatBibi">حیات بی بی</persName>
               <lb/>همشیره مشارالیه ساکن قصبه پیران
               <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName>
               سرکار
               <placeName ref="#mandu">مندو</placeName>
               مضاف
               <lb/>صوبه
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوه</placeName>
               براینمعنی که یکقطعه زمین افتاده بی دار متصل حویلی
               <lb/>تهاکر صاحب از ورثه متروکه بمایان رسیده بود انرا در حالت صحت
               <lb/>نفس و ثبات عقل بلاشرکت غیری که در آن دیگری حقی و
               <lb/>و ملکی ندارد بدست تهاکر
               <persName ref="#pratapChand">پرتاب چند</persName>
               جی و
               <persName ref="#kunwar">کنور</persName>
               جی ولد تهاکر
               <lb/><persName ref="#nihalChand">نهالچند</persName>
               جی ابن تهاکر
               <persName ref="#hamirChand">همیرچند</persName>
               جی چودهری پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               بعیوض مبلغ
               <lb/><measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="10">ده روپیه</measure>
               رایج الوقت که نصف آن
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="5">پنجروپیه</measure>
               تاکیدالاصل میباشد
               <lb/>فروختیم و بیع شرعی کردیم فروختن و بیع کردن صحیحاً شرعیاً جائزاً
               <lb/>نافدا لاشرط فیها و لاخیار ثمن تقابض البدلین فیمابین
               <lb/>واقع و مبلغمذکور از مشتریان مسطور تمام و کمال وصول یافته
               <lb/>در قبض و تصرف خود آوردم و مشتری مذکور را مالک زمین
               <lb/>مذبور نمودیم اگر ثانیا الحال بعد من از اولاد متروکه منمقر دعوی نماید
               <lb/>دروغ و باطل گردد بنابران اینچند کلمه بطریق قباله بدستخط زمینداران
               <lb/>و گواهی همسایگان نویسانیده داده شد که ثانیا الحال سند باشد
               <lb/>تحریر بتاریخ  
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                  بیست و نهم شهر محرم الحرام سنه
                  <num>۱۲۱۹</num></date>
               هجری النبوی 
            </p>
         </div>   
         <div corresp="#orig_div2"  xml:id="trans_div2">  
            <p>
               <lb/>Declared and wholly and lawfully avowed [by] the declarant with the self-same name and lineage: <persName ref="#sultanKhan">Sultan Khan</persName>, 
               <lb/>son of Jahan Khan, son of Chhitur Khan Afghan Ghuri, together with <persName ref="#haiyatBibi">Haiyat Bibi</persName>,  
               <lb/>sister<note>The Persian term used, 'hamshira', literally means of the same milk and implies that <persName ref="#haiyatBibi">Haiyat Bibi</persName> may have been the foster-sister of <persName ref="#sultanKhan">Sultan Khan</persName></note> of the aforementioned, resident in <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pir">pirs</ref>, in the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref> <placeName ref="#mandu">Mandu</placeName> attached 
               <lb/>to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref> <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName>. That one plot of land, which is unused and without any habitation and adjoining the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_haveli">haveli</ref> of 
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="gl_sahib">Sahib</ref>,<note>The reference here is likely to <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <persName ref="#pratapChand">Pratap Chand</persName></note> had come to us by inheritance. That [plot], [we being] in a condition of perfect 
               <lb/>health and sound mind, and there being no rightful and proprietary claim to it, 
               <lb/>[shall be transferred] into the hands of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <persName ref="#pratapChand">Pratap Chand</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref> and <persName ref="#kunwar">Kunwar</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref>, sons of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> 
               <lb/><persName ref="#nihalChand">Nihal Chand</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref>, son of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <persName ref="#hamirChand">Hamir Chand</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, in exchange for the amount of 
               <lb/><measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="10">ten rupees</measure> at the current rate, of which half is confirmed to be <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="5">five rupees</measure>,  
               <lb/>and lawfully sold. The sale, perfectly and legally and permissibly, 
               <lb/>is unconditional and irrevocable, and the price was exchanged between the two of us.
               <lb/>the aforementioned amount from the aforementioned buyers is fully and totally collected, 
               <lb/>and taken into our own possession and custody. And we declared the aforementioned buyers  
               <lb/>to be the owners of the aforementioned land. If henceforth our heirs should make a claim, 
               <lb/>it would be a falsehood and a lie. Accordingly, these words in the form of a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qabala">qabala</ref> with the signatures of the landlords 
               <lb/>and the witnessing of the neighbors have been written such that henceforth it shall be a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sanad">sanad</ref>. 
               <lb/>Written on the date of the <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">29th of Muharram in the Hijri year 1219</date>. 
            </p> 
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="particulars" rend="bottom"><figure place="inspace"><figDesc>rectangle</figDesc></figure>
            <p>
               <figure/>
               <lb/>حد مشرق برآمد دروازه تهاکر صاحب و رسته
               <gap/>
               <lb/>حد جنوبی دیوار صحن حویلی 
               <persName ref="#shivPrashad">شیو پرشاد</persName>
               و 
               <persName ref="#sahibRai">صاحب رای</persName>               
               <lb/>حد مغرب ملحق است دیوار پایگاه تهاکر صاحب
               <lb/>حد شمال دیوار
               <gap/>
               و درخت انبلی
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/><label>طول</label>
               <lb/>
               <g ref="#siyaq">۷</g>
               درعه
               <lb/>درخت انبلی و انار
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/><label>عرض</label> 
               <lb/>
               <g ref="#siyaq">۱۸</g>
               درعه
            </p>
         </div>   
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>
               <figure place="bottom"><figDesc>Rectangle containing text specifying the dimensions of the plot of land being sold and surrounded by further text descrbing the boundaries of the plot.</figDesc></figure>
               <lb/>The eastern boundary comes to the door of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sahib">Sahib</ref><note><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <persName ref="#pratapChand">Pratap Chand</persName></note> and <gap/>
               <lb/>The southern boundary is the wall of the courtyard of the haveli of <persName ref="#shivPrashad">Shiv Prashad</persName> and <persName ref="#sahibRai">Sahib Rai</persName>
               <lb/>The western boundary adjoins the wall of the portico of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_thakur">Thakur</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sahib">Sahib</ref>.
               <lb/>The northern boundary is the wall <gap/> and a tamarind tree.
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/>Length
               <lb/>7 yards
               <lb/>tamarind and pomegranate trees
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/>Width
               <lb/>18 yards
            </p>
         </div>   
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="endorsements" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>العبد
               <lb/><persName ref="#sultanKhan">سلطان خان</persName>
               ولد جهان خان
               <lb/>ابن چهتر خان افغان غوری
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="#haiyatBibi">حیاتی بی بی</persName>
               همشیره مشارالیهه
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>
               <lb/>Servant of God<note>Literally, the slave. This expression is commonly used to indicate the signature, or possibly countersignature, of the person making the declaration.</note>
               <lb/><persName ref="#sultanKhan">Sultan Khan</persName>, son of Jahan Khan,
               <lb/>son of Chhitur Khan Afghan Ghuri
               <lb/>and <persName ref="#haiyatBibi">Haiyati Bibi</persName>, sister of the aforementioned
               <lb rend="empty"/><figure place="margin (right)"><figDesc>spinning wheel</figDesc></figure>
               <figure place="margin (right)"><figDesc>dagger</figDesc></figure>
            </p>   
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="hin" type="witness" rend="bottom right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/><choice>
                  <abbr>सा.</abbr>
                  <expan>साक्ष</expan>
               </choice>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>चो.</abbr>
                  <expan>चोधरी</expan>
               </choice>
               <persName ref="#pratapChand">परताप चंद</persName>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>प्र.</abbr>
                  <expan>परगना</expan>
               </choice>
               <lb/><placeName ref="#pgDhar">धार</placeName> 
               मुसतुरी मजकूर 
               <lb rend="empty"/>
               <lb/>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>सा.</abbr>
                  <expan>साक्ष</expan>
               </choice>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>क||</abbr>
                  <expan>कानूनगो</expan>
               </choice> मीसरी बा-
               <lb/>ई जी <choice>
                  <abbr>प्र||</abbr>
                  <expan>परगना</expan>
               </choice> 
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">धार</placeName>
            </p>
          </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
           <p> 
            <lb/>Witness: <ref type="glossary" target="#gl-chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> <persName ref="#pratapChand">Pratap Chand</persName> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
            <lb/><placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, the aforementioned buyer
            <lb rend="empty"/>
            <lb/>Witness: <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> <persName ref="#misriBai">Misri Bai</persName>
            <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
           </p>   
         </div>     
      </body>
  </text>
